            <div id="content-box-inner-left" style="float: none;">
              <p id="content-header-left">Research</p>
              <p>I have three primary research interests: <span id="stand-out">quantification and visualization of style</span>
               (artistic, literary), <span id="stand-out">applied statistics</span>, and <span id="stand-out">network analysis.
              </p>
              <p>Below is my list of <a href="#pub">publications</a>.
              </p>
              <p>
                You can find information on various projects I'm working on <a href="software.html">here</a>.
              </p>
              <p>
                If you have a question about any of my research, please feel free to 
                <a href="#" onclick="send_mail(); return false;">get in touch with me</a> and I would
                be happy to discuss it with you.
              </p>
              <h3>View my <a href="http://houston.cs.dartmouth.edu/blog">research blog</a>.</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
